      <h1 style="font-size:2.25rem;margin-top:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem">The Best Reciprocating Saws for Cutting Tree Roots & Demolition (2026)</h1>
      <div style="color:#64748b;font-size:0.9rem">June 18, 2026 &middot; 9 min read</div>
